</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Install packages:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>apt-get <span class="nb">install</span> <span class="nt">-y</span> nginx php7.1-fpm php7.1-mysql mariadb-server
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
